title: Enrico Maaßen - Wikipedia
snippet: Enrico Maaßen (born 10 March 1984) is a German professional football manager. He is the current head coach of Swiss Super League side St. Gallen. A FC Anker Wismar youth graduate, Maaßen only played amateur football during his entire career.
